  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0cm 5.75pt 0cm 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapin</span> are a medium=
 sized
  Amphibian with a mix of green and human like skin. <br>
  <br>
  <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapins</span> used to only exist as slaves to the
  Keskudon race, long ago conquered by them. At the same point in history t=
hat
  the <span class=3DSpellE>Keskudons</span> were inexplicably reduced to a =
very
  small part of the Galaxy the <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapins</span> managed=
 to
  separate themselves from their slavery. <br>
  <br>
  <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapins</span> do not age for extremely long period=
s of
  time, so long that it is extremely rare for a <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapi=
n</span>
  to die of old age and it is a very big event amongst <span class=3DSpellE=
>Tarapins</span>
  when one does. Many <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapin</span> hold the marks of=
 their
  slavery on their skin still. This extremely long life time probably helped
  create the myth that a '<span class=3DSpellE>Tarapin</span> never forgets=
'. <br>
  <br>
  <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapins</span> live as familial clans. Each family =
holding
  their name of great importance. The greatest insult a <span class=3DSpell=
E>Tarapin</span>
  uses against another <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapin</span> translates to
  something equal to &quot;May your name die&quot;. The clans do not often
  conflict and many long lasting clan alliances are honoured for generations
  although the primary focus for any <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapin</span> is=
 the
  betterment of their own name.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapins</span> preferred w=
eapon is
  the Missile and they have a Balanced approach with Energy Research.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><i style=3D'mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>This race is=
 trying
  to have a happy population, unlike other races that are like this <span
  class=3DSpellE>this</span> is not just based on taxes and government, it =
is
  largely based on the resources they have available. This makes certain
  planets a lot more valuable to the <span class=3DSpellE>Tarapin</span> th=
an
  others may consider. For the player they will have to consider which plan=
ets
  to take and mines to prioritise based on resources also.<o:p></o:p></i></=
p>
